Copywriter required for an Arabian Adventure..
Copywriter required for an Arabian Adventure..
Location:  --Dubai
Salary:  GBP30000 - GBP50000 per annum + flights, accommodation + TAX FREE income!This role features another great portfolio of brands, with another great agency.
Reporting into a supportive Creative Director, you will be flexing your conceptual brain power for an enviable roster of top brands.
In addition to your writing skills, we're also looking for someone with a great attitude, who can deliver results regardless of whether the budget is large or small and is undaunted by tight deadlines. You will be involved during the creative production process so will be working on film or photo shoots or events, when needed.
Key experience for this role include having a proven track record in creating campaigns within an agency environment and holding demonstrable conceptual thinking skills. You will be able to get to the heart of a brief and deliver the best possible creative solutions. The ability to apply your writing skills to a variety of different mediums that could include scripts, storyboards, emails, guidelines, toolkits and social media. A fantastic portfolio of work that you can show at interview. above all, and be strong communicator who can collaborate with colleagues and client face when needed.
